You can simply ask Alexa to control your SMARTg Home products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “SMARTg Home” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “SMARTg Home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “SMARTg Home” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “SMARTg Home” skill, and you'll be navigated to “SMARTg Home” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on Vacuum
Alexa, turn off Vacuum
Alexa, start Vacuum
Alexa, set Vacuum to wall follow
Alexa, set Vacuum to dock
Alexa, set Vacuum to smart
Alexa, set Vacuum to spiral
Alexa, set Vacuum to high
Alexa, set Vacuum to auto
Alexa, set Vacuum to low
Alexa, what is the battery on Vacuum?
